 &nbsp;<a href="http://forums.crgaming.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=private_message;u=00000121"><img src="http://forums.crgaming.com/eq/priv_message.gif" border='0' alt="Send New Private Message" /></a>&nbsp;
