 &nbsp;<a href="http://forums.crgaming.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=reply;f=9;t=007121;replyto=000043"><img src="http://forums.crgaming.com/eq/quote_ubb6.gif" border="0" alt="Reply With Quote" /></a>&nbsp;
