  Does it warant losing that 7 cha for the 35 hp?  Could that 7 cha made the mez stick?  Could those 35 hp been the difference between life and death?  It's not so cut and dry, and I don't think it will ever be.<P>Like I said, it wasn't my original thought to tell anyone else they were dumb for buying into hp > cha.  It was to tell people that they were idiots for <B>laughing</B> at those of us that didn't.<br /><br />--------------------<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=40436" target="_blank">Tunzell Vigilkeeper</a> -- Phantasmist<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=46656" target="_blank">Zendareth Shatterpast</a> -- 58th Master<br /><a href="http://www.mindspring.com/~aristo/" target="_blank">Order of the Charred Heart</a><br />Innoruuk<br />
