Okay, I&#8217;ve been putting this off cuz I really just didn&#8217;t see the point, but I feel that my hand is being forced.  /ooc direct analysis of Zanithar is coming.  My apologies for those that have attempted to read this thread that was hijacked by this fool. (Yes Zan, I&#8217;m calling you a fool, how you like them apples?)<P>Just FYI Zan, I work many long hours for a fortune 1000 company and a lot of those hours are nights and weekends.  During these times I am pretty much here for support when there&#8217;s a problem with one of our branches, therefore I have a lot of downtime.  So, during this time, I read up on sports (Saints had a great draft!), I also check out a few EQ boards and I do this while listening to KNAC.com.  What&#8217;s your excuse?<P>Okay, my original post was apparently not all that clear, but I fixed that and set the record strait on more then one occasion.  Let&#8217;s take a look at what&#8217;s going on with Zan as this thing takes the downward spiral.  The first few posts are your typical banter, some silly, some not so silly, and some wondering why we have another one of these threads.  Anyway, FeralCom and I exchange a post or two, he gives a blurb on his reasoning, I give a blurb on mine and we&#8217;re not angry with each other, I understand where he&#8217;s coming from, he understands me, we even seem to have some common ground.  Key to this exchange, he <B>read</B> my replies.    <BLOCKQUOTE><font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">quote:</font><HR>In my original post:<BR><B> What&#8217;s really driving me nuts is people that /rofl at others for wearing cha gear, yet they have NO evidence as to why everyone else is so stupid. These people are claiming that they've been reading the boards all the time for years and haven't seen any such tests... Guess they had some kind of filter on.</B><HR></BLOCKQUOTE>    <BLOCKQUOTE><font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">quote:</font><HR>Zanithars&#8217; first post:<BR><B>ROFL ... tell you what, there are a variety of test out there that show charisma has so little effect on mezzes that all that can be proven is that it does affect them. <BR>The tests I have read show anywhere between a 2% and 5% difference. But quite frankly I could care less about finding them, I could care less about reproducing them and I could care less about proving it to you. <BR>I play the way I want and I prefer <BR>1. HP <BR>2. Mana Regen<BR>3. Mana<BR>4. AC<BR>5. Stamina<BR>6. Int<BR>7. Charisma <BR>Could I prove it? Yes, but I am happy with my decision, if you are not then you go prove it. </B><HR></BLOCKQUOTE>There is no thread to prove why I&#8217;m being laughed at, just some kind of justification as to why he&#8217;s not going to show me why I&#8217;m so inferior that I deserve it.  The end of this post is awesome, I&#8217;ve just given 5 independent tests and 2 statements from VI to show why I&#8217;ve taken my stance&#8230; BTW: I&#8217;m not asking for proof from everyone, just those that would openly degrade me for my decisions.  This should be obvious to everyone by now, but I&#8217;ll go over that yet again.    <BLOCKQUOTE><font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">quote:</font><HR>My response:<BR><B>Well, here it is, the first of the 'I'm just better then you, NEENER NEENER' posts. First off, don't laugh at me when you have nothing to support you. Second, your tests don't exist. </B><HR></BLOCKQUOTE>Personally I thought this a rather kind response.  Since someone had obviously not read my threads and still laughed at me.    <BLOCKQUOTE><font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">quote:</font><HR>In Zan&#8217;s 2nd post:<BR><B>You come here you blatently challenge everyone to prove it to you? Who the hell are you and why should I prove it to you? <BR>That is the problem with the world today, nobody willing to do their own leg work. <BR>You amused me because rather than get off your own lazy a$$ and do the tests for yourself you are trying to convince other people to do the work for 